      "acceptanceCriteria": "Benchmark solutions for rotating-frame Navier-Stokes and scalar transport (hemolysis power-law model) must match analytical or published reference solutions within 1% for canonical cases.",
      "rationale": "Code verification performed against Taylor-Couette and lid-driven cavity benchmarks. Hemolysis scalar transport verified against Giersiepen power-law analytical solution. All deviations below 0.8%. Level 2 achieved."
