      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted (3.2M, 8.1M, 18.4M cells). GCI for relative hemolysis index ranged 1.2–3.7% across operating points. Richardson-extrapolated values used for comparison. Required level 2 exceeded; level 3 achieved."
