    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to level 1 and not assessed per MRL 2 requirements with medium model influence. Discretization error exceeded required level (achieved level 3). Output comparison confirms RH index predictions within acceptance tolerance at all operating points. The computational model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the stated COU.",
